### Core Overview

The channel plugin SDK in OpenClaw defines a comprehensive contract for connecting messaging platforms to the OpenClaw agent framework. Channel plugins are **not responsible for their own send/edit/react tools** - OpenClaw maintains a shared `message` tool in core. Instead, plugins own configuration, security, pairing, session grammar, outbound delivery, and threading logic.

